column16: Salvador Perez flies out to left fielder Seth Smith.
Eric Hosmer singles on a line drive to right fielder Will Venable, deflected by first baseman Kyle Blanks.   Alcides Escobar scores.
Alcides Escobar singles on a soft line drive to left fielder Seth Smith.   Jarrod Dyson to 3rd.
Nori Aoki pops out to shortstop Everth Cabrera.
Mike Moustakas lines out softly to shortstop Everth Cabrera.
Danny Valencia grounds into a double play, second baseman Jedd Gyorko to shortstop Everth Cabrera to first baseman Kyle Blanks.   Alex Gordon out at 2nd.
